{"tid":618055,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"youtube 每百萬觀看次數可得$5,000","createTime":"2018-04-05T13:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T13:22:21.000Z","uid":53705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7a2086b99936822a9a610e1a34248ab888ed9f31","tid":618055,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T13:36:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180405/20352498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180405%2F20352498&d=rrgRUdHUxEnNuHX9NDMhlOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=4749d4b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180405%2F20352498&h=9328b3e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180405/20352498</a><br />\n<br />\n咁小?? <br />\n但我見D yuotubee搵十幾萬一個月"},{"pid":"b919346a2aa79aea1b78e830de1717ead8ed7ce3","tid":618055,"uid":43042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T13:37:48.000Z","msg":"跟返你係條片放左幾多廣告"},{"pid":"99fddca534d3fc27efd1de2e23115da324ef6ddb","tid":618055,"uid":81197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a2086b99936822a9a610e1a34248ab888ed9f31","tid":618055,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T13:36:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180405/20352498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180405%2F20352498&d=rrgRUdHUxEnNuHX9NDMhlOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=4749d4b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180405%2F20352498&h=9328b3e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180405/20352498</a><br />\n<br />\n咁小?? <br />\n但我見D yuotubee搵十幾萬一個月"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T13:38:33.000Z","msg":"未計廣告同代言<br />\n同埋人地日日幾條片 累計<br />\n搵到10幾萬真係有可能"},{"pid":"ea201135c46818cf247f714f2801a347d57e0121","tid":618055,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T13:38:36.000Z","msg":"港每百萬觀看次數可得$5,000<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n當局以黃色帆布遮蓋女槍手屍體。互聯網<br />\n【本報訊】YouTube這次槍擊案疑涉分紅糾紛。網絡紅人在YouTube上載自製影片致富不是新鮮事，曾有本港網絡紅人向傳媒透露，YouTube影片每100萬觀看次數可帶來5,000港元收入，不過影片創作者需加入「YouTube合作夥伴計劃」，才可開啟影片的廣告格式，透過廣告賺取收益。<br />\n<br />\n分紅準則不明　無從核數<br />\n<br />\n今年初YouTube將計劃的規例收緊，由本來累積1萬次觀看次數可加入計劃，改為需於過去12個月內有最少1,000個訂戶及4,000個小時的內容，方有營利資格。本地網絡名人司徒夾帶指，最早期使用YouTube時只是想更多人看到其影片，根本沒有營利，後來YouTube才有分紅制度。他表示自己沒有理會分紅，因個人在YouTube平台的分紅金額不算多，「畀幾多（分紅）係佢（YouTube）話事」，形容是YouTube單方面決定分紅金額，他完全不知道數據是如何統計得出，準則不明也無從核數。<br />\n他指YouTube分紅一向有地域之分，香港區分紅不低，但若如女槍手所指逾30萬觀看次數只分得0.1美元（約0.78港元）算偏低，但與其提高分紅透明度，司徒夾帶認為YouTube應增加影片曝光率更為實際。"},{"pid":"dec74b15398d8e69c6c1077b9455e5b41b63ffaa","tid":618055,"uid":168911,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T13:41:51.000Z","msg":"有sponsored video, 品牌代言, affiliate marketing, donations<br />\n單靠youtube ads根本開飯都成問題, 除非你係pewdiepie"},{"pid":"85b324b17dc75b54162e47d66dd2f8d7a0a50e4b","tid":618055,"uid":11310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T13:42:00.000Z","msg":"平時擺d廢片上Youtube 半年都有2000蚊執下，其實真係幾好賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f60dae67cda769c17b738dedf95155b2bfdd5a","tid":618055,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317db68e55e0acd8ae4ae9a1ba62651dc79439fb","tid":618055,"uid":173397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:18:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d49e1a21a55df44eb19852354ce7ef7d71698fc","tid":618055,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:18:46.000Z","msg":"點可以有百萬點擊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1835f8c405dffadf1ce8ff56755b7963b8f1f3","tid":618055,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:22:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}